==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
From the Chinese translation of the biblical phrase "an eye for an eye and a tooth for a tooth" (以牙還牙，以眼還眼)

===Idiom===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' yĭ yá huán yá)
# to take an eye for an eye

